      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Chunking要分成Document Chunking和Code Chunking两个任务。文档分块简单些，5到8秒；代码结构复杂，需要到15秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
